OL,3,CThree men appear in court accused of
OL,4,Cfake 'active shooter' calls to US
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FTwo men from the North West have
OL,8,Fappeared in court charged with making
OL,9,Fhoax calls to US and Canadian police,
OL,10,Fan activity known as swatting.
OL,12,FDylan Ash, 18, from Warrington,
OL,13,FCheshire, and Kieron Ellison, 18, from
OL,14,FSt Helens, Merseyside appeared at
OL,15,FLiverpool Magistrates Court on
OL,16,FThursday. Liam White, 22, from Weston-
OL,17,Fsuper-Mare also appeared.
