OL,7,FAsh and Ellison were subject to bail
OL,8,Fconditions including not to use social
OL,9,Fmedia sites such as Discord, Telegram
OL,10,Fand X, the court heard.
OL,12,FWhite was told not to contact the
OL,13,Fother two defendants.
OL,15,FDetective Sergeant Steve Frame from
OL,16,FMerseyside Police, said: "The charges
OL,17,Fare the culmination of an extensive
OL,18,Finvestigation by Merseyside Police
OL,19,Fworking with US law enforcement,
OL,20,Fincluding the FBI.
